# Quality gates + maintenance sweep

DoD checklist: **`docs/DEVELOPMENT_WORKFLOW.md`** section 4.

## Gates (run after substantive changes)
- Backend: `dotnet test backend/LowCodePlatform.Backend.Tests/LowCodePlatform.Backend.Tests.csproj`
- Frontend: `npm run build` (cwd: `frontend/`)

## Maintenance sweep (when things feel “busy”)
Run before merging larger changes or after backend+frontend milestones:
- Backend compile: `dotnet build` (cwd: `backend/`)
- Frontend compile: `npm run build` (cwd: `frontend/`)

## Drift/duplication watchlist (if repeated 3+ times, propose helper)
- `e?.error?.message ??` (error mapping duplication)
- `observe: 'response'` (header capture patterns)
- `applyServerTimeUtc(` (time sync calls)

## Constraints
- Prefer small, low-risk refactors that preserve behavior.
- If risk grows, split into smaller milestones (still keep WIP=1).

